Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Best bang for your South Boston buck! Anchored by a sleek and stylish kitchen with quartz counters, pendant lighting, and a breakfast bar, this impressive 1-bedroom residence combines quality finishes with an efficient floor plan, offering an outstanding opportunity for a first-time homebuyer, urban professional, or a savvy investor. The open-concept layout maximizes every square foot resulting in an inviting and versatile living area with plenty of space for a table or a work-from-home setup. Additional features include hardwood floors throughout, a comfortable bedroom, and a nicely updated bathroom. Conveniently located a half mile to the Red Line and down the street from favorites like Shy Bird, Castle Island Brewing and Tatte, plus easy access to Thomas Park, Moakley Park, and Carson Beach. A+ value in one of Boston’s most vibrant neighborhoods!
